&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the customer escalation function to ensure fast, empathetic, and consistent issue resolution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop SOPs and escalation protocols to improve quality and reduce refund rates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build out processes to track and improve NPS, CSAT, and retention metrics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Turn escalations into feedback loops that inform process improvements and product enhancements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Process Design &amp;amp; Operational Excellence&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architect and implement new processes to improve counselor performance, student experience, and business efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage CRM and automation tools (HubSpot, etc.) to streamline workflows and maintain data integrity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build reporting systems that provide visibility into counselor utilization, escalation trends, and upsell success&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;New Product &amp;amp; Vertical Launches&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
