&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally across sales, marketing, product, and tech to ensure seamless launches&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure backend systems, counselor training, and customer support are ready to scale with each new launch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
